title: Kunming at Night, 2016.
description: And yet nobody suspects that I'm a shill for the rap industry.  :-/  The mixtape this one comes from can be download for free (legitimately) from Datpiff, but, again, I think it would be more fun to let the comments-section name the vocalist(s) for you.
